summary:
Review of S04E12 – The Stolen Earth

**Show Notes & Links**

* Rose had [experienced regenerations...
caption:
Review of S04E12 – The Stolen Earth

Show Notes & Links

  • Rose had experienced regenerations before
  • The YW remembered Dalek Caan
    • Is there an accepted definition for companions?
  • The YW doesn’t think Adam and Mickey count but
  • But her book says Queen Nefrettiti does
  • The YW had seen Doomsday more recently than Genesis of the Daleks
  • Turns out, it was more than a year of specials
  • In the Time of the Doctor, Eleven said, “Well Number Ten once regenerated and kept the same face. I had vanity issues at the time.”
